{
  "id": "obsidian_full_dev_setup",
  "app": "obsidian",
  "task": "Set up a complete developer vault in the Obsidian vault at /home/user/Documents/FullDevVault.\n\n1. Editor settings: enable `vimMode`, `showLineNumber`, `showFrontmatter`, `strictLineBreaks`; disable `readableLineLength`.\n2. Appearance settings: base font size 15, theme set to 'obsidian' (dark mode).\n3. Hotkey bindings: bind `editor:toggle-bold` ('Toggle bold'), `command-palette:open` ('Open command palette'), and `switcher:open` ('Open quick switcher').\n4. Create folders: 'Projects', 'TIL', 'Snippets'.\n5. Create 'Projects/API-Service.md' with frontmatter `type: project`, `language: python`, `status: active` and body:\n\n```\n# API Service\nREST API built with FastAPI.\n\n## Architecture\n- FastAPI framework\n- PostgreSQL database\n- Redis cache\n\n## Tasks\n- Implement auth endpoints\n- Add rate limiting\n- Set up CI/CD\n\nLearnings: [[TIL-FastAPI]], [[TIL-Docker]]\n#project #python #api\n```\n\n6. Create 'TIL/TIL-FastAPI.md' with frontmatter `type: til`, `date: 2025-03-14` and body:\n\n```\n# TIL: FastAPI Dependency Injection\nFastAPI uses Depends for clean DI.\n\nFrom working on [[API-Service]].\n\n#til #python #fastapi\n```\n\n7. Create 'TIL/TIL-Docker.md' with frontmatter `type: til`, `date: 2025-03-15` and body:\n\n```\n# TIL: Docker Multi-stage Builds\nReduce image size by 70% with multi-stage builds.\n\nApplied to [[API-Service]].\n\n#til #docker #devops\n```\n\n8. Create 'Snippets/Python-Decorator.md' with frontmatter `type: snippet`, `language: python` and body:\n\n```\n# Python Decorator Pattern\n\nUseful in [[API-Service]] for auth middleware.\n\n#snippet #python\n```",
  "env": {
    "files": []
  },
  "verification": [
    {
      "command": "check-setting /home/user/Documents/FullDevVault vimMode true",
      "key": "match",
      "expected": true,
      "description": "Vim mode enabled"
    },
    {
      "command": "check-setting /home/user/Documents/FullDevVault showLineNumber true",
      "key": "match",
      "expected": true,
      "description": "Show line number enabled"
    },
    {
      "command": "check-setting /home/user/Documents/FullDevVault showFrontmatter true",
      "key": "match",
      "expected": true,
      "description": "Show frontmatter enabled"
    },
    {
      "command": "check-setting /home/user/Documents/FullDevVault readableLineLength false",
      "key": "match",
      "expected": true,
      "description": "Readable line length disabled"
    },
    {
      "command": "check-setting /home/user/Documents/FullDevVault strictLineBreaks true",
      "key": "match",
      "expected": true,
      "description": "Strict line breaks enabled"
    },
    {
